val.title: East County Hall of Justice (Alameda County Courthouse)

Applicant.name: Alameda County Surplus Property Authority
Applicant.address: 224 W. Winton Avenue, Room 110, Hayward, CA 94544

val.description: The East County Hall of Justice (Alameda County Courthouse) is a 196,219 square foot building comprised of 13 courtrooms, offices, and associated facilities on 22 acres located at 5149 Gleason Drive. The project is under construction and is anticipated to be complete in Spring 2017.
